## A Unified, Scalable, and Accessible Framework

::: {.panel-tabset group="language"}
### Pipline
```python
from BI import bi

# Setup device------------------------------------------------
m = bi(platform='cpu') # cpu, gpu or : tuple

# Import Data ------------------------------------------------
m.data(data_path) 

# Define model ------------------------------------------------
def model(arg1,argb2):
   pass

# Run mcmc ------------------------------------------------
m.fit(model) 

# Summary ------------------------------------------------
m.summary()

# Diagnostics ------------------------------------------------
m.diag()
```

